    subsets←{⌿∘⍵¨↓⌽⍉2⊥⍣¯1⊢¯1+⍳2*≢⍵} ⍝ (From APLCart) Powerset: All subsets of ⍵, including the empty set (0⌿⍵) and ⍵ itself

    ⍝ Interpreter version information
    isClassic←82=⎕dr''
